headline: Generative AI Meets Beauty: Ulta’s (ULTA) Bold Bet On Nvidia’s (NVDA) Hairstyling Tech
summary: Ulta Beauty has launched an AI app that lets users use their selfies to show instant and realistic previews of their favorite hairstyles. The app is accelerated by Nvidia’s StyleGAN2 generative AI technology which helps create the near-perfect, realistic versions of yourself to apply the changing hairstyles to.
